text: haey chaur puok anak kom yk peaky samboth robsa puok anak mk baok banhchhot rveang puok anak cheaheto thveu aoy cheung rel kraoypi mean pheap rung moam haey noh aoy saoh . haey puok anak nung phloksa rosacheate akrak ( tondakamm knong lokey nih) daoysaarte puok anak ban reareang anak dtei pi meakra robsa a l laoh . haey puok anak nung ttuol tearounakamm yeangothngonthngor bamphot
